    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my reliable ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in solid condition and has been well-maintained, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great and runs smoothly, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
