    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54 inline-six power plant, equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission to a variable M-differential lock. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including double-VANOS servicing and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural rigidity of the chassis. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the suspension geometry remains tight and the engine pulls with linear urgency. Ideal for the driver seeking the analog feedback and 50/50 weight distribution of a true performance icon.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
