    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of pride in ownership, striking a perfect balance between daily utility and refined style. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish that catches the light beautifully, showing only the minor, honest character marks one would expect from careful road use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin where the upholstery remains supple and the dashboard looks nearly new. Every button, switch, and feature functions exactly as intended, from the ice-cold climate control to the premium sound system. Mechanically, this car is in its prime; it has been strictly maintained according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a smooth, responsive drive and a quiet engine. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and confident. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering many miles of reliable and comfortable service.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presenting a sophisticated vehicle that exemplifies reliability and performance. This model has been meticulously maintained to ensure a seamless driving experience, offering a refined interior and a robust mechanical profile. It represents an exceptional balance of luxury and value for the discerning driver who demands quality without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
