      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my awesome car. It\u2019s been so reliable and is in really wonderful shape\u2014perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways! I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it honestly drives like a dream. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great on the road, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery and a visceral 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains sharp and composed, utilizing the M-Variable differential lock and Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for precise turn-in and exceptional lateral stability. Meticulously maintained with a focus on preventative care\u2014including addressed throttle actuators\u2014this high-revving icon offers a pure mechanical connection and communicative steering feedback. The exterior displays minor road-derived patina consistent with spirited driving, while the cabin retains excellent bolster support and tactile integrity. A quintessential driver\u2019s specification for those who prioritize atmospheric induction and German engineering precision.",
